entries.femaleVariant: I was going to call you. I prepared an ofrenda for Jaquito. We can't let him go without a proper goodbye.
The ceremony will be at the Coyote Cojo. Many of his friends will be there.
I'll be there, too.
Do my best to make it, too.
Say no more, Mama Welles. I'll be there.
Do my best to make it.
Mhm. Do your best…
<kiroshi l="mex" o="Ahí te veo, V." t="See you, V." b="" a=""/>
V? Good to hear you. Finally.
Been a long time since we talk. Since when Jackie pass away.
Wanted to offer my condolences.
How're you doing?
Sorry, really should've called.
I'm sorry, I-- I should've called before.
entries.maleVariant: Sorry, I-- I should've called before.

entries.femaleVariant: Yes, you should have. But better late than never, hm?
How're you doin'?
Callin' to offer my condolences.
Hm, I did not doubt it for a second.
Hm. "Offer your condolences."
Don't know if that's something for me.
<mothertongue l="mex" m="Jesucristo" b="" a=" V, you lived under our roof!"/>
How you think? My son is dead.
Don't know that that's... somethin' for me.
entries.maleVariant: I don't know that... that's something for me.

entries.femaleVariant: It is for you. So you can say goodbye. Like a human being.
V? Hm, been a long time since you call... Since Jackie passed away.
You had other important things on your mind, hm?
But I am hanging in there.
Have the decency not to treat me like some stranger you just met!
Just wanted to know how you're holding up.
Um... just wanted to explain why I didn't, y'know...
Just wanted to know how, you know, you were holdin' up.
Wanted to call you before, Mama Welles, but... Eh, you know how it is…
entries.maleVariant: Wanted to call you before, Mama Welles, but, uh... y-you know how it is…

entries.femaleVariant: <mothertongue l="mex" m="Mi vida" b="" a=", what's the matter?"/>
Wanted to explain myself.
I suppose you still do what you... hehh, what you did before.
No good, V. Parents should not bury their own children. Hmm, and I can't even do this.
It's OK, V. You don't need to. I know how things are.
I was with Jackie when he...
V, listen. This is the path my son chose. He knew what he signed up for.
<mothertongue l="mex" m="mija" b="Just promise me you won't get yourself killed, OK? May He watch over you, " a="."/>
entries.maleVariant: <mothertongue l="mex" m="mijo" b="Just promise me you won't get yourself killed, OK? May He watch over you, " a="."/>

entries.femaleVariant: <mothertongue l="mex" m="Mira" b="" a=", don't worry. I take care of myself."/>
If he could have been saved, you would have done it, I know.
